FARMING GUIDE:
_|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___
___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|_
_|___|                                                     |_|___
___|_|  FARMING GUIDE:                                     |___|_
_|___|  ⦿ You are need to have seeds to farm.              |_|___
___|_|  ⦿ You can only plant a maximum of 50 seeds.        |___|_
_|___|  ⦿ Farming cost hours, energy level, increase       |_|___
___|_|    hunger level when planting and harvest.          |___|_
_|___|  ⦿ NOTE:                                            |_|___
___|_|    » If you forgot to harvest the crops on time,    |___|_
_|___|      some of crops starting to withered.            |_|___
___|_|    » You can't plant on WINTER!                     |___|_
