ENERGY AND HUNGER LEVEL:
_|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___
___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|_
_|___|                                                     |_|___
___|_|  ENERGY AND HUNGER LEVEL GUIDE:                     |___|_
_|___|  ⦿ Ways to decrease Energy and increase Hunger:     |_|___
___|_|        Farming, Mining                              |___|_
_|___|  ⦿ Ways to replenish Energy and decrease Hunger:    |_|___
___|_|        Eating food, Rest, Go to Saloon.             |___|_
_|___|_____________________________________________________|_|___
___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|_
