LIVES:
_|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___
___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|_
_|___|                                                     |_|___
___|_|  LIVES:                                             |___|_
_|___|  ⦿ You are given 3 hearts.                          |_|___
___|_|    Losing 3 hearts means Game Over.                 |___|_
_|___|  Conditions:                                        |_|___
___|_|  ⦿ You must maintain your Energy level above 0.     |___|_
_|___|  ⦿ You must maintain your Hunger level below 100.   |_|___
___|_|  ⦿ You must Rest before the Time reaches 24:00.     |___|_
_|___|_____________________________________________________|_|___
___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|_
