THE TOWN:
_|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___
___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|_
_|___|                                                     |_|___
___|_|  THE TOWN:                                          |___|_
_|___|  ⦿ In the Market Place:                             |_|___
___|_|      You can buy seed, sell crops, sell gold.       |___|_
_|___|      Everyday the cost changes randomly.            |_|___
___|_|  ⦿ In the Saloon:                                   |___|_
_|___|      You spend money to drink till midnight.        |_|___
___|_|      After, it resets to the next day.              |___|_
_|___|_____________________________________________________|_|___
___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|_
_|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___


GUIDELINES:
 ⦿ There are 4 seasons (Spring, Summer, Fall, Winter)
 ⦿ Each seasons have 30 days.
 ⦿ Each day have 24-hour format.
 ⦿ You are only given a max Crops count of 500
    and gold count of 200.



 LIVES:
 ⦿ You are given 3 hearts.
       Conditions:
       ⦿ You must maintain your Energy level above 0.
       ⦿ You must maintain your Hunger level below 100.
       ⦿ You must Rest before the Time reaches 24:00
 

